    <ThingDef ParentName="HP_AoD_OnSkinBase">
        <defName>GW_SM_FibroVest</defName>
        <label>fibrovest</label>
        <description>The Astartes fibrovest acts as a vital conduit, connecting the Space Marine's nervous system to their power armor. This neural interface enables a seamless integration of the Marine's movements and reflexes with the capabilities of the armor, enhancing combat prowess and responsiveness. Beyond mere control, it provides sensory feedback, allowing the Marine to feel and react to their surroundings intuitively. This link between mind and machine is fundamental to the effectiveness of Astartes warriors on the battlefield, enabling them to operate at peak efficiency in the most demanding combat situations.</description>
        <recipeMaker>
            <researchPrerequisite>GW_SM_AstartesFabrication</researchPrerequisite>
        </recipeMaker>
        <graphicData>
            <texPath>Things/OnSkin/FibroLayer/FibroLayer_Male_south</texPath>
        </graphicData>
        <apparel>
            <wornGraphicPath>Things/OnSkin/FibroLayer/FibroLayer</wornGraphicPath>
            <tags>
                <li>GW_SM_FibroVest</li>
            </tags>
        </apparel>
